There is ‘huge interest’ in the
Middle East bond market, V. Shankar, Standard Chartered Plc’s,
chief executive officer for the Middle East, Europe, Africa and
the Americas, said. He spoke in an interview today with
Bloomberg Television in Marrakesh, Morocco.  To contact the reporter on this story:
